PEOPLE ex rel. DEXTER v. PALMER et al. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. May 8, 1894.) Proceeding by the people on the relation of Orrando P. Dexter against Elijah A. Palmer and others, as assessors.

Argued before MAYHAM, P. J., and PUTNAM and HERRICK, JJ.

No opinion. Order reversed, case to be returned to special term to be heard upon the merits, upon the appellant’s paying $50, and printing and •other disbursements of this appeal.
